data.description: Welcome to a charming MULTI-GENERATIONAL Mount Dora residence! This 'last house' on the block comes with a .34 acre lot with a 1,900+ sqft 2 bedroom 2 bathroom home, a 1 bedroom/1 bathroom attached in-law suite with private entrance, and a separate workshop. The flexible layout provides endless possibilities for accommodating guests, extended family, or creating private office space. Your outdoor space is the perfect spot for outdoor dining, relaxation, or entertaining guests.  This home sits just a mile away from downtown shopping and entertainment, yet feels like its in the county. Whether you're looking for a full-time residence or an investment opportunity, this property is short-term rental friendly, allowing you to maximize its potential. Roof was replaced in 2022 and the tankless water heater replaced in 2023. Schedule your showing today!
